<text top="177" left="90" width="5" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="177" left="126" width="329" height="17" font="3">This statement will be issued as a document of the </text>
<text top="195" left="90" width="337" height="17" font="3">Security Council under the symbol S/PRST/2002/30. </text>
<text top="132" left="468" width="10" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="132" left="504" width="334" height="17" font="3">The Security Council has thus concluded the </text>
